		<title>Microsoft To Fund Mistral’s European AI Expansion in Multibillion-Dollar Deal</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/microsoft-funds-mistrals-european-ai-expansion/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ekemini]]></dc:creator>
