					<description><![CDATA[<p>Cross-border shopping and digital finance are moving faster than ever before. In a major move for global expansion, Ant International raises $1.2 billion in its Series A equity funding round.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/ant-international-raises-1-2-billion-for-global-scaling/" data-wpel-link="internal">Ant International Raises $1.2 Billion To Fuel Global Scaling &amp; AI Commerce Solutions</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span>Cross-border shopping and digital finance are moving faster than ever before. In a major move for global expansion, Ant International raises $1.2 billion in its </span><a href="https://www.ant-intl.com/en/news/detail/?id=ant-international-raises-approx-USD1_2-billion-in-series-a-equity-financing-to-boost-cross-border-payments-agentic-commerce-solutions-for-global-businesses&amp;redirect=news&amp;tag=" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span>Series A equity funding round</span></a><span>. The funding will fuel the global scaling and technology advancement of Ant International. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Demand for seamless cross-border payments continues to skyrocket worldwide. Since spinning out as an independent operating business back in 2024, the company has transformed into a vital backbone for international commerce and cross-border payment processing.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Ant International To Power Seamless Cross-Border Payments Everywhere</span></h2>
<div id="attachment_203663" style="width: 970px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203663" class="size-full wp-image-203663" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Ant-International.jpg" alt="Ant International announced the successful closing of its Series A equity financing. Credit: © 2026, Ant International " width="960" height="642" /><p id="caption-attachment-203663" class="wp-caption-text">Ant International Announces $1.2bn Series A</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Cross-border selling has long presented frustrating technical and financial hurdles for small businesses and large online merchants. Ant International actively solves these friction points by building direct bridges between disjointed digital payment markets. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Today, the platform connects more than 150 million merchants to a vast network of over two billion user accounts across Asia, Europe, the Middle East and Latin America. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">By partnering with regional financial institutions, card networks, and mobile wallet providers, the company streamlines currency conversion and checkout flows. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The new Series A capital will help scale this underlying transaction infrastructure much faster. As a result, local shop owners can seamlessly accept localized digital payment methods from global travelers and cross-border shoppers without facing high overhead costs.</span></p>
<p><b><i>More Updates: </i></b><a href="https://ventureburn.com/natural-raises-30m-agentic-payments-infrastructure/" data-wpel-link="internal"><b><i>Natural Raises $30M to Build Payments Infrastructure for AI Agents</i></b></a></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Expanding the Four Core Financial Pillars</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Ant International delivers its global service network through four specialized operational business units. Every single pillar addresses a distinct challenge in cross-border trade and financial inclusion:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400"><b>Alipay+: </b><span style="font-weight: 400">Connects international merchants directly to over dozens of local digital wallets and mobile banking apps worldwide.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400"><b>Antom:</b><span style="font-weight: 400"> Supplies customized merchant acquiring services and payment processing infrastructure for digital commerce businesses.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400"><b>WorldFirst:</b><span style="font-weight: 400"> Provides multi-currency business accounts, rapid foreign exchange, and trade payment services for cross-border sellers.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400"><b>Bettr:</b><span style="font-weight: 400"> Offers microloans and flexible credit products designed specifically to empower small and medium enterprises.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Together, these four core platforms connect more than 150 million online and offline merchants to roughly two billion active user accounts across global markets.</span></p>
<p><b><i>More Updates: </i></b><a href="https://ventureburn.com/legendspace-raises-29-5-million-ai-rocket-engines/" data-wpel-link="internal"><b><i>LegendSpace Raises $29.5M To Develop AI-Driven Rocket Engines</i></b></a></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Deploying Agentic AI for Smarter Global Trade</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Artificial intelligence is a major focus of the new investment round. Ant International is moving beyond traditional payment. It will be routing by heavily investing in agentic AI capabilities for modern commerce. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">These autonomous algorithms actively handle complex financial tasks. Ant International is looking into Agentic AI used in optimizing FX rates, predicting cash flow spikes, and automating seller risk assessments in real time. Cybersecurity remains another crucial priority for the company. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Ant International continues to refine its proprietary AI security tools to protect digital transactions against sophisticated deepfake fraud and cyber threats. The company is using smart automation to give small businesses sophisticated tools that were used by only a few of the world&#8217;s largest corporations.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Supporting Inclusive Financial Growth in Emerging Markets</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">While emerging economies are the fastest growing frontier in global e-commerce, millions of micro-entrepreneurs are still not able to access credit in sufficient quantities. Ant International aims to fill this gap with its digital ecosystem.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">By combining local mobile payment connections with predictive AI credit scoring, the firm helps small sellers establish verifiable financial histories and gain fast access to working capital loans. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">This Series A funding solidifies Ant International&#8217;s position as an essential catalyst for international digital commerce. The company remains committed to building an open, accessible payment architecture where merchants of any size can effortlessly operate and grow across borders.</span></p>
<p><b><i>More Updates: </i></b><a href="https://ventureburn.com/cuspai-raises-450-million-series-b-ai-materials-foundry/" data-wpel-link="internal"><b><i>CuspAI Raises $450M To Launch AI Materials Foundry</i></b></a></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/ant-international-raises-1-2-billion-for-global-scaling/" data-wpel-link="internal">Ant International Raises $1.2 Billion To Fuel Global Scaling &amp; AI Commerce Solutions</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
